nload images</p>\n</p><a href="https://easydigitaldownloads.com/extensions/download-image-watermark/?ref=1" title="Download Image Watermark" class="button-secondary">Get this Add On</a></div><div class="edd-extension"><h3 class="edd-extension-title">Cardsave Gateway</h3><a href="https://easydigitaldownloads.com/extensions/cardsave-gateway/?utm_source=plugin-addons-page&#038;utm_medium=plugin&#038;utm_campaign=EDDAddonsPage&#038;utm_content=CardsaveGateway" title="Cardsave Gateway"><img width="320" height="200" src="https://easydigitaldownloads.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/03/edd-cardsave-320x200.png" class="attachment-showcase wp-post-image" alt="edd-cardsave" title="Cardsave Gateway" /></a><p><p>Adds a payment gateway for Cardsave to Easy Digital Downloads</p>\n</p><a href="https://easydigitaldownloads.com/extensions/cardsave-gateway/?ref=1" title="Cardsave Gateway" class="button-secondary">Get this Add On</a></div>', 'no'),
